data.meta_description:
15 likes, 0 comments - simbasible on October 6, 2020: "Where’d You Go, Bernadette is terribly paced and structured with the film’s third act being horribly rushed. Still, the main performance from Cate Blanchett is reliably outstanding, the title character is so well developed and the overall movie, though messy, is very sweet and moving.

My Rating - 3.5
